    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am Ahmed Adel, and I regularly travel by your trains. I am writing this letter to you because I have lost my laptop on the train during my last trip.",
        "The first point I want to raise is the laptop which I have lost is valuable. Not only is my laptop expensive, but also all of my work is stored in it. It is HP silver laptop with a medium screen size, and its charger is beside it.",
